{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2019/12/31/为WindowsTerminal2添加gitBash的profile.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"宫不上叔"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"29f11cbf-52e1-518a-af09-653735985f0d","excerpt":"为Windows Terminal 2添加git bash的profile 粘贴以下代码到settings中。","html":"<h1>为Windows Terminal 2添加git bash的profile</h1>\n<p>粘贴以下代码到settings中。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"guid\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"{00000000-0000-0000-ba54-000000000002}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"commandline\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\\\"%PROGRAMFILES%\\\\git\\\\usr\\\\bin\\\\bash.exe\\\" -i -l\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Bash\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"startingDirectory\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"%USERPROFILE%\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"icon\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ms-appx:///ProfileIcons/{0caa0dad-35be-5f56-a8ff-afceeeaa6101}.png\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2019/12/31/为WindowsTerminal2添加gitBash的profile.html","date":"December 31, 2019","title":"为WindowsTerminal2添加gitBash的profile"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2019/12/31/为WindowsTerminal2添加gitBash的profile.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/plan/2019/12/30/2019年终总结.html","title":"2019年终总结"},"frontmatter":{"category":"plan"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/01/03/2019年的Node测试最佳实践.html","title":"2019年的Node测试最佳实践"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}